OL,3,CCalls grow for whole life terms to be
OL,4,Cextended to under-18s
OL,6,FThe government has said it is not
OL,7,Flooking at extending whole life orders
OL,8,Fto criminals under the age of 18,
OL,9,Fdespite growing calls for this to
OL,10,Fchange following the sentencing of the
OL,11,FSouthport killer.
OL,13,FAxel Rudakubana was sentenced on
OL,14,FThursday to a minimum of 52 years for
OL,15,Fthe murders of nine-year-old Alice da
OL,16,FSilva Aguiar, Bebe King, six, and
OL,17,FElsie Dot Stancombe, seven, as well as
OL,18,Fthe attempted murder of eight children
OL,19,Fand two adults.
