OL,6,F"The last government did reduce it to
OL,7,F18 - which is part of international
OL,8,Flaw that threshold - because the
OL,9,FManchester Arena bomber was too young
OL,10,Fto qualify. That still stands.
OL,12,F"But on the other changes that may be
OL,13,Frequired to our laws, our agencies
OL,14,Fthat missed the chances to stop this
OL,15,Fman, or the programmes that are there
OL,16,Fto try to prevent atrocities like
OL,17,Fthis, the prime minister has said very
OL,18,Fclearly no changes are off the table."
