OL,6,FReferring to the judge who sentenced
OL,7,FRudakubana, Healey added: "He's made
OL,8,Fclear that he doesn't expect this man
OL,9,Fto come out of prison - I hope that'll
OL,10,Fbe the case. I expect that'll be the
OL,11,Fcase."
OL,13,FDowning Street said it shares "the
OL,14,Fpublic disgust at these barbaric
OL,15,Fcrimes" and the desire "for this vile
OL,16,Foffender to never be on our streets
OL,17,Fagain".
OL,19,FHowever, it confirmed that extending
OL,20,Fwhole life orders is not something it
OL,21,Fis looking at currently.
